OL,3,CCouncil goes ahead with stricter
OL,4,Cplanning controls for second homes
OL,6,FIt is peak tourist season at seaside
OL,7,Ftowns and beauty spots across Wales
OL,8,Fand of those visiting the country,
OL,9,Fsome may dream of one day having a
OL,10,Fpermanent base here for their holidays.
OL,12,FBut that's about to get more difficult
OL,13,Fin Gwynedd, where the council is going
OL,14,Fahead with a controversial initiative
OL,15,Fto force people to get planning
OL,16,Fpermission for a second home or short-
OL,17,Fterm let.
