OL,3,CCouncil goes ahead with stricter
OL,4,Cplanning controls for second homes
OL,6,FGwynedd resident Glenis Bisson said: "
OL,7,FI have lost sales and I've lost them
OL,8,Fbecause of Article 4 coming in. How
OL,9,Fdoes that make me feel? Angry. But
OL,10,Fthat wasn't my first emotion. It was
OL,11,Fdesolation."
OL,13,FIf you own a home, you have some basic
OL,14,Frights to make changes to it, and
OL,15,Fthese are called Permitted Development
OL,16,FRights.
