OL,3,CCouncil goes ahead with stricter
OL,4,Cplanning controls for second homes
OL,6,FUnder these rules, you can make
OL,7,Fchanges like building a small
OL,8,Fextension or making your home a shared
OL,9,Fhouse for up to six people without
OL,10,Fasking for planning permission.
OL,12,FIn Wales, second homes and holiday
OL,13,Fhomes have different classifications
OL,14,Ffrom regular residential homes:
OL,16,FThe Welsh Government brought in these
OL,17,Fclassifications to control the number
OL,18,Fof second homes in holiday hotspots.
