OL,3,CCouncil goes ahead with stricter
OL,4,Cplanning controls for second homes
OL,6,FArticle 4 is a planning rule that
OL,7,Flocal authorities can bring in to take
OL,8,Faway a particular permitted
OL,9,Fdevelopment right, in a particular
OL,10,Flocation. That means you would have to
OL,11,Fapply for planning permission.
OL,13,FWhat does the council say?
OL,15,FGwynedd Council leader Dyfrig Siencyn
OL,16,Fsaid of Article 4: "This is something
OL,17,Fwe have been calling for for many
OL,18,Fyears, for decades.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
