OL,3,CCouncil goes ahead with stricter
OL,4,Cplanning controls for second homes
OL,6,F"This now gives us an opportunity to
OL,7,Fdo that in order to control the
OL,8,Fsubstantial growth in short-term lets
OL,9,Fand second homes in places like
OL,10,FGwynedd.
OL,12,F"It will give us an element of control
OL,13,Fon the use of dwellings in our county.
OL,15,F"Our housing stock has dropped because
OL,16,Fwe are losing housing stock to second
OL,17,Fhomes and short-term lets. Airbnb has
OL,18,Fbeen a great part of that.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
