OL,3,CCouncil goes ahead with stricter
OL,4,Cplanning controls for second homes
OL,6,F"It's one more opportunity for us to
OL,7,Fhave some control on that second-home
OL,8,Fissue, which prevents local people
OL,9,Ffrom gaining access to the property
OL,10,Fmarket."
OL,12,FAsked for his message to opponents of
OL,13,FArticle 4, he said: "There are many
OL,14,Fpeople opposed to Article 4, and we've
OL,15,Fhad an enormous response to the
OL,16,Fconsultation last year. We have gone
OL,17,Fthrough those responses very carefully
OL,18,Findeed, meticulously so, and we've
OL,19,Fclassified them into themes and we
OL,20,Fhave sought to respond to them in a
OL,21,Flogical manner.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
