OL,6,F"When we think that we need further
OL,7,Finformation or advice, we have gone
OL,8,Fout to seek that.
OL,10,F"We have looked at the effect of
OL,11,Fsimilar situations to Article 4, for
OL,12,Finstance in Edinburgh, to see if it
OL,13,Fhas effect on the market, etc.
OL,15,F"We believe we have answered the
OL,16,Fquestions that have been posed by that
OL,17,Fconsultation, and we believe there is
OL,18,Finsufficient evidence to show that it
OL,19,Fwill have the effect that they fear."
